formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The amount of construction cost has been considered on the basis of the information provided by the competent authorities of the Corporation.
2.	Total number of units to be constructed has been assumed to be built up evenly.
3.	We have not been provided with the details of the amounts received from the beneficiaries towards the houses allotted to them. Hence, as and when such details will be provided, we will verify the same and subsequently report the same too.
4.	As informed by the management, Rs.7500/- is received in the general bank account from beneficiaries at the time of form submission and hence, the same is considered as RECEIVED AMOUNT in Form-3(Annexure).
5.	The agreement execution is under process in many of the beneficiaries. As and when it will be executed and verified by us, the same will be reported by us.
